uint32_t CAN_DCANEccErrSts_t::messageNum

Message Object number where single bit error has occured. Valid when CAN_getOptions with (DCAN_ECC_ERROR_STATUS) is called. Not valid when CAN_getOptions with (DCAN_ECC_DIAG_ERROR_STATUS) is called.
